00:04:09.360 --> 00:04:12.630
You might have also, you know,
another completely legitimate

00:04:12.630 --> 00:04:15.720
way to do this problem-- let me
write it this way-- so our

00:04:15.720 --> 00:04:21.779
original problem is P is equal
to 2l plus 2w-- is on this

00:04:21.779 --> 00:04:25.960
right-hand side, what if
we factor out a 2?

00:04:25.960 --> 00:04:27.010
So let me make this clear.

00:04:27.010 --> 00:04:30.280
You have a 2 here, and
